      "text": "[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778145612,
      "updated": 1778145616
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc594d00000000005b27a9",
      "text": "　スクレイピングとかと何が違うんだろう、と考えたり",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778145614,
      "updated": 1778145636
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc596300000000005b27ab",
      "text": "　https://note.com/teramotodaiki/n/n70b07bbacbb3?sub_rt=share_pb",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778145636,
      "updated": 1778145638
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc596500000000005b27ac",
      "text": " 　devin注文やAIを使った予約、営業電話とかと何が違うんだろう",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778145638,
      "updated": 1778145672
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc598700000000005b27ae",
      "text": " 　スパムメール系は法律で禁止されてた気がする（曖昧）",
